<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Smart Estaciona</title>
    <style>

        * {
            padding: 0;
            margin:0 ;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Franklin Gothic Medium', 'Arial Narrow', Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        @media (min-width:320px){
            h2 {
                font-size: 18px;
                margin: 20px;
                text-align: center;
                font-family: 'Franklin Gothic Medium', 'Arial Narrow', Arial, sans-serif;
            }
        }
        @media (min-width:1024px){
            h2 {
                font-size: 30px;
                text-align: center;
                font-family: 'Franklin Gothic Medium', 'Arial Narrow', Arial, sans-serif;
            }
        }

        @media (min-width:320px){
            .container {
                display: grid;
              margin-left: 10px;
              margin-right: 10px;
              
            }
        }
        
        @media (min-width:1024px){

            .container {
            border: 2px solid black;
            padding: 15px;
            width: 1000px;
            height: 700px;
            margin: 100px auto;
            border-bottom: 15px solid           rgba(152, 138, 138, 0.519);
               
            }
        }
        

        @media (min-width:320px){
            .logo-estaciona {
                width: 300px;
                margin-top:20px;
            }
        }
        @media (min-width:1024px){
            .logo-estaciona {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                width: 500px;
                box-shadow: 0px 10px 20px 10px rgba(0, 128, 0, 0.275);
            }
        }

        @media (min-width:320px){
            .header {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                width: 320px;
                gap: 10px;
            }
        }
        @media (min-width:1024px){
            .header {
                display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 36px;
            background-color: rgba(152, 138, 138, 0.357);
            padding: 10px;
            width: 100%;
            flex-direction: row;
            }
        }
        


         @media (min-width:320px){
            .header ul {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                justify-content: left;
                list-style: none;
                gap: 10px;
                width: 300px;
              
            }
        }
            @media (
                min-width:1024px){
            .header ul {
                width: 30vw;
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: row;
                justify-content: space-between;
                list-style: none;
                gap: 40px     
            }
        }
        
        .header ul  li {
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-color: rgb(103, 233, 103);
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        @media (min-width:320px){
            .header ul li {
                padding: 10px;
                font-size: 14px;
                }  
            }
            @media (min-width:320px){
            .header ul li {
                padding: 20px;
                font-size: 18px;
                }  
            }
        
        .header ul li:hover {
            background-color: rgba(103, 233, 103, 0.647);

        }

        @media (min-width:320px){
            .section {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
        @media (min-width:1024px){
            .section {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        }
        }

        .painel{
            font-size: 20px;
            width: 200px;
            height: 180px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .disponiveis {
            border-radius: 5px;
            color:rgb(22, 8, 18);
            margin: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 10px 20px 10px rgba(64, 207, 64, 0.581);
            background-color: rgb(103, 233, 103);
        }

        .ocupadas {
            margin: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0px 10px 20px 10px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.421);
            background-color: rgb(241, 72, 72);
        }
        h3 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
           
        }

        .vagas {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;    
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;   
        }

        @media (min-width:320px){
            .vagas {
                margin-top: 20px;
                width: 300px;
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items:center;
            }
        }
        .card {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .card p {
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: rgb(103, 233, 103);
        }
        @media (min-width:320px){
                .card p {
            font-size: 18px;
            width: 300px
        
            }
        }

        @media (min-width:1024px){
            .card p {
                font-size: 22px;
            width: 90%;
            margin: auto;
            
            }

        }
        .card p > span {
            color:rgb(249, 250, 255);
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>

</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>SMART ESTACIONA</h2>
            <ul>
                <li> Nossos Contatos</li>
                <li>Cadastrar Novo Cliente</li>
            </ul>
         </div>
         <div class="section">
            <div class="card">
                <img  class="logo-estaciona" src="undraw_city_driver_re_9xyv.svg" alt="">
                <p>Bem vindo ao <span>Smart-Estaciona</span> um software de controle de stacionamento <span>inteligente</span>, que facilita sua vida através de mordernidade e <span>tecnologia em gestão</span></p>
            </div>

            <div class="vagas">
                <h3> PAINEL DE VAGAS</h3>
                <div class="painel ocupadas">
                    <p>VAGAS OCUPADAS</p>
                    <p>15</p>
                </div>

                <div class="painel disponiveis">
                    <p>VAGAS DISPONÍVEIS</p>
                    <p>20</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            </div>
         </div>
        
    </div>
    
</body>
</html>